freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Itchy neck when I woke up, probably due to higher levels of cortisol first thing in the morning. I took my Vital Nutrients Aller-C, and did not need anything else. Every day I need to take a 1-2 hour nap, just because I am sleepy - not exhausted, for I have plenty of energy when I am awake and I feel very healthy. Just sleepier than normal.
Some itching on my neck and both thumbs (near thumb joints that are slightly arthritic.)
